{
  "texts": [
    "Text datasets focus on language topics, general knowledge, logic and lifestyle.",
    "Previous data collection work focuses predominantly on describing datasets by their task compositions 5, 11, 17, but rarely by their actual topics (except ref.",
    "14 in their appendix).",
    "Extended Data Table 1b shows the most popular topics, clustered by category, with their representation across datasets.",
    "Like most NLP tasks, much of these text data focus on communication and language understanding topics, followed closely by general knowledge, routine, sports and education."
  ]
}